---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="最新消息 - 澎湖慢活．角落民宿">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-800 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">最新消息</h1>
      <p class="text-xl">掌握民宿最新資訊與優惠活動</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <article class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v4m-6 4V9a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v2M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
              </svg>
              2025年12月
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">包棟優惠活動進行中！</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              為了提供更好的住宿體驗，我們推出包棟優惠方案！適合大家庭或團體出遊，享受整棟民宿的私人空間。
            </p>
            <p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold">
              詳情請來電洽詢：0988-089913
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v4m-6 4V9a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v2M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
              </svg>
              常態性服務
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">貼心服務項目</h2>
            <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>• 代購當地土產服務</li>
              <li>• 免費精緻早餐</li>
              <li>• 加床服務（沙發床）</li>
              <li>• 嬰幼兒用品：奶瓶消毒鍋、嬰兒澡盆</li>
              <li>• 兒童遊戲床</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-gray-500 mb-4">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v4m-6 4V9a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v2M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
              </svg>
              重要提醒
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">預訂注意事項</h2>
            <div class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <p>📞 <strong>訂房時間：</strong>早上10:00 - 晚上10:00</p>
              <p>💰 <strong>訂金：</strong>房價的30%，請於3日內匯款</p>
              <p>📋 <strong>匯款後：</strong>請務必來電告知帳號後五碼</p>
              <p>⏰ <strong>改期政策：</strong>請於7日前通知，可保留房間三個月</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-blue-600 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">想了解更多資訊？</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8">歡迎隨時與我們聯繫</p>
      <a href="/contact" 
         class="bg-white text-blue-600 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
        聯絡我們
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout> 